    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54B32 power plant with perfectly calibrated individual throttle bodies and a seamless Double VANOS system. This example boasts a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The chassis integrity is paramount; the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the suspension geometry remains true with fresh bushings and factory dampers. The exterior retains its original factory depth with no panel variance, while the interior features pristine Nappa leather with zero bolster compression. Mechanically synchronized and aesthetically flawless, this M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated longitudinal engineering.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
