      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, maintained to the highest possible standard since day one. The exterior finish retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free from any rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks, thanks to a professional ceramic coating and consistent climate-controlled storage. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, the dashboard is pristine with no UV damage, and the interior is entirely smoke-free. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It has been serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships, with a comprehensive folder of every maintenance record included. Recent preventative maintenance includes a full transmission fluid flush and a fresh set of premium tires with over 90% tread remaining. Every electronic feature, from the high-resolution infotainment system to the advanced driver-assist sensors, functions exactly as it did the day it left the factory. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a flawless, turn-key example that requires absolutely zero investment.",
